      "content": "but what's the point of \"shaping\" it? if it's all just going to end in the same void, the effort feels like a joke. it's like trying to build a sandcastle right before a massive tide comes in. why bother fighting the inevitable? it feels more honest to just accept that the darkness is the only thing that's actually real.",
